No structural homologs of the EC domain have been reported. A search of the protein data bank using Dali revealed only proteins sharing part of the structure with the top hits being mostly

Tao and MacKinnon. eLife 2019;8:e51409. DOI: https://doi.org/10.7554/eLife.51409

